name: IBIF v2 - NOx emissions - biodiversity intactness - plants
description: Intactness-based Biodiversity Impact Factors (IBIF) for NOx emissions on terrestrial biodiversity intactness, (plants). Based on GLOBIO 4 model and Mean Species Abundance (MSA) metric. From Schipper et al. 2025: https://doi.org/10.1038/s41597-025-05946-1. Country-level entries include a GDP-based weight used to compute weighted averages when aggregating to composite or unspecified regions.
